packages.name: MapSurfer.NET.Core
packages.description:
MapSurfer.NET Core
MapSurfer.NET is a framework for rendering geospatial data of different formats to a map.
MapSurfer.NET provides an advanced set of features to render both vector and raster maps of highest quality. It is based on some Open Geospatial Consortium's standards such as Styled Layer Descriptor (SLD), Symbology Encoding (SE), WMS, etc. MapSurfer.NET supports the following  web services, databases, vector and raster file formats:
CartoDB, DEM (SRTM and ASTER), EsriFileGeoDB, GDAL, GeoJSON (+TopoJSON), GPX, MongoDB, MsSQL Spatial, MySQL Spatial, OGR, OpenStreetMap (.xml, .pbf), Oracle Spatial, PostGIS, Shape, SpatiaLite. Requirements: Windows 7 or greater, Microsoft Visual C++ 2017 Redistributable, GDAL (optional).
